block se1
    h2.title Digital Technical Publications
    p.txt With the average vehicle car parc age getting older - in the US it is circa 11.8 years, Germany 9.8 years and Russia 13 years - upkeep of existing vehicles will require higher maintenance investment. This means access to comprehensive repair and maintenance information from the OEM. 

block se2
    h2.title Challenge
    p.txt Right to repair is a hot button topic across a number of industries - including automotive. OEM's are responsible for providing technical parts and service information to its own network, customers and independent repair facilities - either through technical portals and websites for its franchised service points or online subscription services for the independent aftermarket.

block se3
    h2.title Solution
    p.txt Getac Automotive delivers vehicle code details, non-emission related information, re-programming or flashing for all makes and models, directly to the technician's rugged device - improving vehicle servicing and repair efficiency - to create a seamless technician experience.

block se4
