        li <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Confidential technical information secured with Getac optional features such as RFID, Device Monitoring and multi- factor authentication.
        li <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Stand up to any workshop task with built-rugged construction and seamless software.
        

